{"tid":552711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天災回顧] 1999年9月21日凌晨1時47分 台灣中部7.3級大地震","createTime":"2018-02-06T18:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T11:06:07.000Z","uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4bd8cda93754bdb38e9340c5f6b367a88a9a8bed","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/20b624b4f5668aef26c6741ffa56ed23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F20b624b4f5668aef26c6741ffa56ed23.jpg&h=a0e578c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n921大地震，又稱集集大地震，是1999年9月21日上午1時47分發生於台灣中部山區的逆斷層型地震，造成台灣全島均感受到嚴重搖晃，共持續約102秒。震央位於北緯23.85度、東經120.82度，處於南投縣集集鎮境內，震源深度約8.0公里，黎克特制7.3級（美國地質調查局測得矩震級7.6－7.7級），相當於約45顆廣島原子彈的威力。<br />\n<br />\n此地震造成2,415人死亡，29人失蹤，11,305人受傷，51,711間房屋全倒，53,768間房屋半倒。不但人員傷亡慘重，也震毀許多道路與橋樑等交通設施、堰壩及堤防等水利設施，以及電力設備、維生管線、工業設施、醫院設施、學校等公共設施，更引發大規模的山崩與土壤液化災害。<br />\n<br />\n由於台中縣市、南投縣為主震央區域，故受災特別嚴重。死亡人數最多為台中縣1138人，次多為南投縣928人，有40845棟房屋全倒、41373棟半倒（包含多處各級學校校舍）。地震造成的房屋建築損毀以南投縣和台中縣市最為嚴重，兩縣市之房屋全倒與半倒的總戶數約佔全台損壞戶數的95% 。<br />\n<br />\n集集大地震引發比同年729全台大停電更嚴重的電力設施受損，因南投縣中寮鄉之中寮超高壓變電所遭震損，加上有高壓電塔倒塌毀損，造成全台灣於地震發生後立即停電，共計649萬戶無電可用。台電公司動員全體員工全力搶修之後，採限電措施，直到10月10日始解除全台限電。<br />\n<br />\n全台工商業活動全面停擺，尤其新竹科學工業園區損失最為慘重，全球科技產業零組件供應也因此遭受到波及。估計經濟損失達新台幣3,647億元。<br />\n<br />\n921地震時造成近千座橋樑中，約有20%之橋樑受到不同程度之損傷，其中20餘座橋被列為嚴重損壞 。台鐵西部幹線一度全面停駛，亦有多數客運公司暫時停駛。<br />\n<br />\n921大地震的死傷程度有紀錄以來僅次於1935年的新竹台中大地震（關刀山地震）。為悼念地震逝去的民眾與警惕自然災害的威脅，中央政府於2000年訂立每年9月21日為「國家防災日」，並舉行地震演習，以求災害來臨時能做好防護措施，將傷亡的可能降至最低。"},{"pid":"a2bf4d2ef860fc0d31674a0a973b2e46d7da8f83","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gu-NrrGzRZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgu-NrrGzRZQ&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e01a96fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gu-NrrGzRZQ</a><br />\n台灣921大地震發生原因 1/3"},{"pid":"f44524c2d5d5305b5b7fff577b3d1d77beecf30b","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:53:51.000Z","msg":"地下兩層，樓高12層的東星大樓倒塌是台北市受災最嚴重， 87人罹難，為傷亡人數最多的獨棟大樓。而位於新莊市「博士的家」由於未按圖施工，建築安全系數未達一半標準，不堪四級地震而導致3棟大樓倒塌，45人罹難。 <br />\n<br />\n在台北地區，地震造成的災害與效應特別嚴重。科學家估計是由於台北盆地四面環山，會導致地震波聚集效應，再加上台北盆地土質鬆軟所致的場址效應，使烈度放大的現象更形劇烈。"},{"pid":"ec08b867240477cafc3a6aec92b881b080bfea24","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:54:29.000Z","msg":"此外921地震後，在全台灣誘發超過21,000處的崩塌地，受影響面積達11300公頃，造成中台灣廣大面積區域土石鬆動。<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，地震後造成的土石鬆動讓觸發土石流所需要的雨量遠低於地震前；震後一年所需的雨量僅需震前的四分之一，震後七年仍只需震前雨量的二分之一。<br />\n<br />\n2001年侵襲台灣的桃芝颱風挾帶而來的豪雨在中台灣就造成655起土石流。2009年颱風莫拉克侵襲台灣引發的88水災原因之一也可能是921大地震。"},{"pid":"6772a9618179475f14fe627c1d176f3668f7ef5b","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T18:55:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xv8xgEeQ-rQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXv8xgEeQ-rQ&d=BHXERQ%2Buve8Ngw6OonVBHsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ce03b2c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xv8xgEeQ-rQ</a><br />\n台灣啟示錄 921 十年特輯 1/8"},{"pid":"30c377bcb1993629e5ed41efe277fc1abdb9e9cd","tid":552711,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d13871ab5226e027f4852380e959b6393464762","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T19:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/12d731df088029c5df7060cbf65775be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F12d731df088029c5df7060cbf65775be.jpg&h=30bcbdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a2ed588f104d338326ed8b1135e8f500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa2ed588f104d338326ed8b1135e8f500.jpg&h=fa77fd8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8ed991e2355316cebfd13ff29ef947fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F8ed991e2355316cebfd13ff29ef947fa.jpg&h=324d735a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af073809c49c27c99dbb92369263062380b02e5d","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b353e7a2c783754a5bfd16d8bb1f3fa143a58c00","tid":552711,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fd11c36affafba25033da531458f7b2695212ed","tid":552711,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:20:55.000Z","msg":"多難興邦"},{"pid":"44cd7045474e68da498141e429dd551dc0f85204","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324acc8f476e86794a204a292f9c17718eed1111","tid":552711,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"果陣發現大量樓都係偷工減料用豆腐渣起<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/news/transform/20160206/-GZo-fxpfhzn5732169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fnews%2Ftransform%2F20160206%2F-GZo-fxpfhzn5732169.jpg&h=644903c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d60e92ee79c1a7277635b17a002d67462560469","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/e2180e74fa6db6050f8aed1b5a394bf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fe2180e74fa6db6050f8aed1b5a394bf0.jpg&h=27973824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/70c5b85bbe20b850b8e284a6e84c09d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F70c5b85bbe20b850b8e284a6e84c09d2.jpg&h=6f2fe653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埤豐橋位於豐原市與東勢鎮交界的大甲溪段，因921地震斷層經過橋的南端，造成南側橋頭（靠近豐原）斷落，上游側河床抬升約6公尺，錦水頁岩出露，形成牆面與瀑布。"},{"pid":"ce67825f7d76844a2d24b6f07aac6c6963fe8101","tid":552711,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5ba1502b34976e215e8096da7547abc16002e30","tid":552711,"uid":57962,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fc8b6bb901277c1bb82322d58b24b18863127c5","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2ab7866c10ee6375c7b80304297f04b0a2527e","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a175083b85a34b19f678c4eadff1adca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa175083b85a34b19f678c4eadff1adca.jpg&h=c4479f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n石岡壩位在豐原往東勢的路上，建於1974年，原為大甲溪的攔河堰，全長700多公尺，是臺中市的主要水源區。<br />\n<br />\n因921地震斷層通過，造成壩體第15至18道閘門斷裂受損，垂直崖高達9.8公尺，現被保留設立成921地震紀念公園（石岡斷壩公園）。"},{"pid":"a2b4a62878de88e4411c6b21cee93903d3ae14f1","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa455974bf2179fa4059c44d88a5c363d716f22e","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T08:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434a31700673c95703e9ef5ab15e32c8e1019a77","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/9793d30f53763edec5f0a09da8d4c232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F9793d30f53763edec5f0a09da8d4c232.jpg&h=deb115f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01db08e6cc4bebeb1c9d2da49a7e44bdf35959e4","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d85a3bbaa5a56fc292c5ec62d26e073e6ea530","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd311d640710474ee6f6432fc17b96361edc645e","tid":552711,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b353e7a2c783754a5bfd16d8bb1f3fa143a58c00","tid":552711,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T19:37:15.000Z","msg":"台狗"},{"pid":"b571fd49591064199c8e7cdd1c81e729de5a4e7d","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185e1cba0cf07136d4b8cf531ef3d405189c52f6","tid":552711,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/7936cb04847d0ff35c954d79ad60b946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F7936cb04847d0ff35c954d79ad60b946.jpg&h=a36c45ca&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}